{"tid":57684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川婦街市買排骨黑暗中現藍光　疑因含磷超標","createTime":"2016-12-28T08:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T17:00:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8300491b74749ae6dbc8eac06c880f511e6899","tid":57684,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161228/photo/bkncn-20161228110258231-1228_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161228123405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161228%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161228110258231-1228_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161228123405&h=bcd7c277&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四川綿陽市有市民發現在當地街市購買的排骨，竟泛出幽幽藍光，引起民眾恐慌。蘇女士的母親上周五在街市的肉檔購買了2.5公斤排骨，其母隨後把排骨用花椒及食鹽醃製後，再掛在露台風乾，到了晚上再取下放到籃子內。周日凌晨，蘇女士的母親赫見桌上有一片藍光，開燈後始知原來是排骨發光。蘇女士隨後在網上翻查相關報道，大多表示發光的豬肉不宜食用。她又到購買排骨的肉舖理論，惟店方卻否認豬肉是從其攤檔出售。 <br />\n<br />\n北京、重慶、上海等地近年均有市民買到「藍光豬肉」。但對於豬肉發光的成因，各方說法不一，曾有專家指，是由於豬隻被餵食過量含磷飼料，使體內含磷量超標，導致身體發出藍光，不建議食用。另有說法指，發光是由於「螢光假單胞菌」作怪，但細菌對人體影響不大，徹底煮熟豬肉即可。"},{"pid":"247cf4a26c0cce8655cb99fd1962029f5b708841","tid":57684,"uid":55090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:18:20.000Z","msg":"好恐怖呀"},{"pid":"efd7b186c468e6fe553cd5f8d012c36e1200d3dc","tid":57684,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76eed886ad08cf3a4fbf275bf0edb833d75765d","tid":57684,"uid":26477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"估唔到排骨都有出Blueray<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f0aedf2e3827a5114c6cdb9b96eda24e84b60e","tid":57684,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"特色黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf71660740e6ce2fbb5e3caf79a31e1101feb696","tid":57684,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"藍光高清豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8874428108590c04dc5dc9cb19111806a531e356","tid":57684,"uid":36540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:36:55.000Z","msg":"藍到咁都可以攞嚟賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cf7e67609610c2dd2e83ae824c9789fc1f5a95","tid":57684,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4882e48301e32e1667e409ab0216aa535a4b92a","tid":57684,"uid":47500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"豬肉都有psycoframe <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a4ae0222b2fd7fd11dfe761d0084fff097a03b","tid":57684,"uid":55789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"識發光可以賣貴d"},{"pid":"b8bc9f9a61f871d4a0ca6f447cd68190e73e5885","tid":57684,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"唉，你噉樣「座」（做）係無用㗎，好似你呢啲咁「猝」（出）色嘅「難」（男）人，無論匿埋喺邊，都好似漆黑之中嘅螢火蟲一樣，咁鮮明，咁「猝」（出）眾。你憂鬱嘅眼神，唏噓嘅鬚根，神乎奇技嘅刀法，同埋嗰杯 Dry Martini&hellip;&hellip;都已經將你深深噉「猝」（出）賣咗。雖然你係咁「猝」（出）色，但係行有行規，無論點，你都要找埋尋晚條過夜數，叫雞唔使畀錢呀！？"},{"pid":"9a63eba1be642756a1b3e960317b65f89653b2af","tid":57684,